data.text:
Gombe, Nigeria

Latitude and longitude coordinates are: 10.283333, 11.166667.

Gombe is a large city in Nigeria, with the population exceeding 260,000 people. The city is the capital of the Gombe Emirate and is a local cultural and educational center. Unfortunately, for the last few years the criminal situation in the city has worsened and there were a few suicide bombing accidents in 2014-2015.
